---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于 - C雙G">
  <div class="about-container">
    <h1>关于</h1>
    <p>这里是 C雙G 的个人站点，记录技术成长、生活随记与家庭故事。</p>
    <p>用 <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank">Astro</a> 构建，部署在 GitHub Pages。</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
